---
layout: base.njk
title: "Writing Services — Refine, Write, or Special Request"
description: "Professional writing help for wedding vows, toasts, retirement speeches, and letters — Refine editing, Write from scratch, or a Special Request for a highly custom occasion. Always written in your voice."
---
{% from "icons.njk" import check %}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / Writing Services</p>
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Writing Services</span>
      <h1>Sometimes a workbook isn't quite enough.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        For speeches, toasts, letters, and vows that need a more personal hand, our writers work
        directly with you — listening carefully, then helping you shape what you already know
        you want to say. Every package is built around your voice, not ours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card reveal" id="refine">
        <h3>Refine</h3>
        <p class="pricing-card-desc">You've already written something. We help you make it better.</p>
        <p class="pricing-card-price">$59</p>
        <ul class="pricing-card-features">
          <li>{{ check() }} Full edit for grammar, flow, and clarity</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} Feedback on emotional impact and pacing</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} Voice preserved — we edit, we don't rewrite</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} One round of revision notes</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} 3–5 business day turnaround</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-block" href="/contact/">Start Refine</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card is-featured reveal reveal-delay-1" id="write">
        <span class="pricing-card-badge badge badge-accent">Most Popular</span>
        <h3>Write</h3>
        <p class="pricing-card-desc">Written from scratch, in your voice, from your own answers.</p>
        <p class="pricing-card-price">$149</p>
        <ul class="pricing-card-features">
          <li>{{ check() }} Guided questionnaire about your story</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} First draft written entirely from your answers</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} One full round of revisions included</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} Matched to your tone — sincere, funny, or both</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} 5–7 business day turnaround</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-accent btn-block" href="/contact/">Start Write</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-2" id="special-request">
        <h3>Special Request</h3>
        <p class="pricing-card-desc">A highly custom service for an occasion not covered in our workbook series.</p>
        <p class="pricing-card-price">$299</p>
        <ul class="pricing-card-features">
          <li>{{ check() }} Detailed questionnaire to gather information about the occasion and audience</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} One full round of revisions</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} Typically 5–7 day turnaround (varies based on length and subject)</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} Optional add-ons including priority turnaround and an extra round of revisions</li>
          <li>{{ check() }} Well suited for anniversary party speeches, award acceptance speeches, marriage proposals, eulogies, and similar occasions</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-block" href="/contact/">Start Special Request</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-muted reveal" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
      Every package includes our confidentiality guarantee and unlimited grammar and clarity
      passes within your revision window.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="featured-testimonial reveal">
      <div class="featured-testimonial-photo">
