      </div>
      <div class="featured-testimonial-quote">
        {% from "icons.njk" import quoteMark %}
        {{ quoteMark("icon-quote") }}
        <blockquote>
          "I put off writing my best man speech for weeks because I had no idea where to start.
          I answered a handful of questions about how Danny and I met and some of our favorite
          stories, and a few days later I had a draft that already sounded like me — I just
          smoothed a few lines and practiced it twice. Standing up at the reception was the least
          stressful part of the whole wedding."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-person">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder" style="background: var(--slate);">JM</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Jordan M.</div>
            <div class="testimonial-detail">Best man speech, Denver, CO</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

